hadiths[33]{hadithnumber,text}:
1773,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik Umra ke baad doosra Umra donon ke darmyan ke gunahon ka kaffara hai aur Haj mabroor ki jazaa jannat ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hai.
1774,"Ikrima bin Khalid ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se Haj se pahley Umra karne ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha koi harj nahi, Ikrima ne kaha ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj karne se pahley Umra hi kya tha aur Ibrahim bin Sad ne Muhammad-bin Ishaq se bayan kya, unse Ikrima bin Khalid ne bayan kya ke maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha phir yahi hadis bayan ki. ham se Amr bin Ali iflaas ne bayan kya, unse abu-Aasim ne bayan kya, unhein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di, unse Ikrima bin Khalid ne bayan kya ke maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
1775,"main aur Urwa-bin-Zubair masjide-Nabawi mein dakhil huey, wahan Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ke paas baithey huey they, kuchh log masjide-Nabawi mein ishraaq ki Namaz padh rahe they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham ne Abdullah-bin-Umar se un logon ki us Namaz ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke bidat hai, phir unse puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitney Umerey kiye they? unhon-ne kaha ke chaar, aik unmein se rajab mein kya tha, lekin ham ne pasand nahi kya ke unki is baat ki tardeed karein."
1776,"ham ne Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre se unke miswak karne ki awaz suni to Urwa ne puchha aey meri maan ! aey Ummul-Momenin ! abu-Abdur-Rehman ki baat aap sun rahi hain? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha wo kya keh rahe hain? unhon-ne kaha keh rahe hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char Umerey kiye they jin mein se aik rajab mein kya tha, unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah abu-Abdur-Rehman par raham karey ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to koi Umra aisa nahi kya jis mein wo khud maujood na rahi hon, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajab main to kabhi Umra hi nahi kya."
1777,maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha to aap ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajab mein koi Umra nahi kya tha.
1778,"maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitney Umerey kiye they? to aap ne farmaya ke char , Umra Hudaibiya Zi-Qada mein jahan par mushrekeen ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rok diya tha, phir aainda saal Zi-Qada hi mein aik Umra qaza jiske mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mushrekeen se suleh ki thi aur tesraa Umra Jaarana jis mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghaaliban Hunain ki ghaneemat taqseem ki thi, chotha Haj ke sath maine puchha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj kitney kiye? farmaya ke eik."
1779,maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Umra ke mutaalliq puchha to aap ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Umra wahan kya jahan se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mushrekeen ne wapas kar diya tha aur doosrey saal (usii) Umra Hudaibiya (ki qaza ( ki thi aur aik Umra Zi-Qada main aur aik apne Haj ke sath kya tha.
1780,jo Umra Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne Haj ke sath kya tha iske siwa tamam Umerey Zi-Qada hi mein kiye they. Hudaibiya ka Umra aur doosrey saal uski qaza ka Umra tha. (kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quran kya tha aur Hijjatul-wada se mutaalliq hai) aur Jaarana ka Umra jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Hunain ki ghaneemat taqseem ki thi. phir aik Umra apne Haj ke sath kya tha.
1781,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Haj se pahley Zi-Qada hi mein Umerey kiye they aur unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maah Zi-Qada mein Haj se pahley 2 Umerey kiye they."
1782,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Ansari khatun (umme-Sanaan (rz)) se (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unka naam bataya tha lekin mujhey yad na raha ( puchha ke to hamarey sath Haj kyon nahi karti? wo kehney lagi ke hamarey paas aik oont tha, jis par Abu-Fulaan (yani iska khaawind) aur iska betaa Sawar ho kar Haj ke liye chal diye aur aik oont unhon-ne chhoda hai, jis se pani laya jata hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha jab Ramazan aaey to Umra kar lena kyonke Ramazan ka Umra aik Haj ke barabar hota hai ya usi jaisi koi baat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmai."
1783,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina se nikley to Zil-Hijja ka chaand nikalney wala tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi Haj ka ehram baandhna chahta hai to wo Haj ka baandh ley aur agar koi Umre ka baandhna chahta hai to wo Umre ka baandh ley. agar mere sath qurbani ka janwar na hota to main bhi Umre ka ehram baandhtaa . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke ham mein kuchh ne to Umre ka ehram baandha aur kuchh ne Haj ka ehram baandhaa. mein bhi un logon mein thi jinhoney Umre ka ehram baandha tha, lekin Arfa ka din aaya to main us waqt haaiza thi, chunanche maine uski Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Umra chhod de aur sar khol de aur is mein kangha kar ley phir Haj ka ehram baandh lenaa. (maine aisa hi kya) jab Muhassab mein qiyam ki raat aai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman ko mere sath taneem bhejaa, wahan se maine Umre ka ehram apne us Umre ke badle mein baandha (jis ko tod daala tha) ."
1784,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko apne sath sawari par ley jayen aur taneem se unhein Umra kara laaein . Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kahin yun kaha maine Amr-bin-Dinar se suna, kahin yun kaha maine kai baar us hadis ko Amr-bin-Dinar se suna."
1785,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ashaab ne Haj ka ehram baandha tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa qurbani kisi ke paas nahi thi. un hi dinon mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yaman se aaey to unke sath bhi qurbani thi. unhon-ne kaha ke jis cheez ka ehram Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandha hai mera bhi ehram wahi hai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ko (Makka mein pahunch kar) uski ijazat de di thi ke apne Haj ko Umra mein tabdeel kar dein aur Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa w Marwa ki saee karke baal tarashwa lein aur ehram khol dein, lekin wo log aisa na karein jinke sath qurbani ho. is par logon ne kaha ke ham Mina se Haj ke liye is tarah se jaeinge ke hamarey zakar (private part) se mani tapak rahi ho. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo baat ab hui agar pahley se malum hoti to main apne sath qurbani ka janwar na laataa aur agar mere sath qurbani ka janwar na hoti to (Umra ada karney ke baad) main bhi ehram khol deta. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (is Haj mein) haaiza ho gaee thin isliye unhon-ne halaanki tamam manaasik ada kiye lekin Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kya. phir jab wo paak ho gain aur tawaaf kar liya to kaha ya Rasulullah ! sab log Haj aur Umra donon karke wapas ho rahe hain lekin main sirf Haj kar saki hon, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke unhein sath lekar taneem jayen aur Umra kara laaein , ye Umra Haj ke baad Zil-Hijja ke hi maheene mein hua tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab jamara Aqba ki rami kar rahe they, to Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! kya ye ( Umra aur Haj ke darmyan ehram khol dena ( sirf aap hi ke liye hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke hamesha ke liye hai."
1786,"mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di unhon-ne kaha ke Zil-Hijja ka chaand nikalney wala tha ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina se Haj ke liye chaley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo Umre ka ehram baandhna chahey wo Umre ka baandh ley aur jo Haj ka baandhna chahey wo Haj ka baandh ley , agar main apne sath qurbani na laataa to main bhi Umre ka hi ehram baandhtaa , chunanche bahut se logon ne Umre ka ehram baandha aur bahuton ne Haj kaa. main bhi un logon mein thi jinhoney Umre ka ehram baandha tha. magar main Makka mein dakhil honey se pahley haaiza ho gaee, Arfa ka din aa gaya aur abhi main haaiza hi thi, iska ronaa main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rooii , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umra chhod de aur sar khol ley aur kangha kar ley phir Haj ka ehram baandh lenaa, chunanche maine aisa hi kya, iske baad jab Muhassab ki raat aai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath Abdur-Rehman ko taneem bheja wo mujhey apni sawari par peechhey bitha kar le gaey wahan se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne apne (chhodey huey) Umerey ke bajaey doosrey Umre ka ehram baandha is tarah Allah Taala ne unka bhi Haj aur Umra donon hi poorey kar diye na to uske liye unhein qurbani laanii padi na sadqa dena padaa aur na roza rakhna padaa."
1787,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! log to Haj aur Umra karke wapas ho rahe hain aur maine sirf aik Haj kiya hai? is par unse kaha gaya ke phir intizar karein aur jab paak ho jayen to taneem ja kar wahan se (Umra ka ( ehram baandhein, phir ham se falan jagah aa milein aur ye ke us Umre ka sawab tumharey kharch aur mehnat ke mutabiq milega."
1788,"Haj ke mahinon aur aadaab mein ham Haj ka ehram baandh kar Madina se chaley aur maqam sarf mein padao kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab se farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani na ho aur wo chahey ke apne Haj ke ehram ko Umra mein badal de to wo aisa kar sakta hai, lekin jiske sath qurbani hai wo aisa nahi kar sakta. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ashaab mein se kuchh maqdoor walon ke sath qurbani thi, isliye unka ( ehram sirf ( Umre ka nahi raha, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey to main ro rahi thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke ro kyon rahi ho? maine kaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab se jo kuchh farmaya main sun rahi thi, ab to mera Umra reh gaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya baat huii? maine kaha ke main Namaz nahi padh sakti (haiz ki wjah se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke koi harj nahi, to bhi Adam ki betiyon mein se aik hai, aur jawan sab ke muqaddar mein likha hai wahi tumhara bhi muqaddar hai. ab Haj ka ehram baandh ley shayad Allah Taala tumhen Umra bhi naseeb kare. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Haj ka ehram baandh liya phir jab ham (Haj se farigh ho kar aur) Mina se nikal kar Muhassab mein utrey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman ko bulaya aur unse kaha ke apni behan ko haram ki had se bahar ley ja ( taneem (taake wo wahan se Umre ka ehram baandh lein, phir tawaaf w saee karo ham tumhara intizar yahin karengey. ham aadhi raat ko aap ki khidmat mein pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya farigh ho gaey? maine kaha haan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad apne ashaab mein kooch ka elaan kar diya. Baitullah ka tawaaf wadaa' karne waley log subah ki Namaz se pahley hi rawaana ho gaey aur Madina ki taraf chal diye."
1789,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jaarana mein they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik shakhs hazir hua jubba pahney huey aur is par khalooq ya zardi ka nishan tha. usne puchha mujhey apne Umre mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis tarah karne ka hukm detey hain? is par Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ki aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kapda daal diya gaya, meri badi aarzoo thi ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahiy nazil ho rahi ho to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhun. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya yahan aao Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jab wahi nazil ho rahi ho, us waqt tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhney ke aarzoomand ho? maine kaha haan! unhon-ne kapdey ka kinara uthaya aur maine usmein se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap zor-zor se kharraatey ley rahe they, mera khayal hai ke unhon-ne bayan kya ''jaisey oont ke saans ki awaz hoti hai'' phir jab wahi utarnii band hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke poochhney wala kahan hai jo Umra ke barey mein poochhta tha? apna jubba utaar de, khalooq ke asar ko dho daal aur) zafran ki) zardi saaf kar ley aur jis tarah Haj mein kartey ho isi tarah ismein bhi karo."
1790,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se puchha jabke abhi main nau-umr tha ke Allah Taala ka irshad ''Safaa aur Marwa donon Allah Taala ki nishaniyan hain isliye jo shakhs Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey uske liye unki saee karne mein koi gunah nahin'' isliye main samajhta hun ke agar koi unki saee na karey to is par koi gunah na hoga. ye sun kar Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke hargiz nahi. agar matlab ye hota jaisa ke tum bata rahe ho phir to unki saee na karne mein waqei koi harj nahi tha, lekin ye aayat to Ansar ke barey mein nazil hui hai jo manaat but ke naam ka ehram baandhtey they jo qudaid ke muqabil mein rakha hua tha wo Safa aur Marwa ki saee ko achchha nahi samajhtey they, jab Islam aaya to unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha aur is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai ke ''Safaa aur Marwa donon Allah ki nishaniyan hain isliye jo shakhs Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karey uske liye unki saee karne mein koi gunah nahin'' Sufiyan aur abu-Muawia ne Hisham se ye zyadti nikaalii hai ke jo koi Safa Marwa ka phera na karey to Allah uska Haj aur Umra pura na karega ."
1791,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umra bhi kya aur ham ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Umra kya, chunanche jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley (Baitullaah ka ( tawaaf kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham ne bhi tawaaf kya, phir Safa aur Marwa aaey aur ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aaey. ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Makka walon se hifazat kar rahe they ke kahin koi kaafir teer na chala de, mere aik sathi ne ibn-abii-Aufii se puchha kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba mein andar dakhil huey they? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi."
1792,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke mutaalliq kya kuchh farmaya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke aap ne farmaya tha '' Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ko jannat mein aik mautaa ke ghar ki bashaarat ho, jis mein na kisi qism ka shor w ghul hoga na koi takleef hogii.''"
1793,"ham ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein malum kya jo Umre ke liye Baitullah ka tawaaf to karta hai lekin Safa aur Marwa ki saee nahi karta, kya wo (sirf Baitullah ke tawaaf ke baad) apni biwi se ham-bistar ho sakta hai? unhon-ne iska jawab ye diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka) tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baitullah ka saat (7) chakkaron ke sath tawaaf kya, phir maqaame-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ke qareeb 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, iske baad Safa aur Marwa ki saat (7) martaba saee ki ''aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi tumharey liye behtreen namoona hai.''"
1794,ham ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi iske mutaalliq sawal kya to aap ne farmaya Safa aur Marwa ki saee se pahley apni biwi ke qareeb bhi na jana chahiye
1795,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Batha mein hazir hua aap wahan (Haj ke liye jatey huey utrey huey they) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya tumhara Haj hi ka irada hai? maine kaha, ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha aur ehram kis cheez ka baandha hai? maine kaha maine usi ka ehram baandha hai, jiska Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram baandha ho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tu ney achchha kya, ab Baitullah ka tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee kar ley phir ehram khol daal, chunanche maine Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee, phir main banu-Qais ki aik aurat ke paas aaya aur unhon-ne mere sar ki juein nikaaliin, iske baad maine Haj ka ehram baandhaa. main (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad) usi ke mutabiq logon ko masla bataya karta tha, jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ka daur aaya to aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke hamein kitabullah par amal karna chahiye ke usmein hamein (Haj aur Umra) pura karne ka hukm hua hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat par amal karna chahiye ke us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ehram nahi khola tha jab tak qurbani ke janwar ki qurbani nahi ho gaee thi. lihaza qurbani ka janwar sath laney walon ke waastey aisa hi karne ka hukm hai."
1796,"Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam Abdullah ne unse bayan kya, unhon-ne Asma (Raziallahu anha) se suna tha, wo jab bhi hajoon pahaad se ho kar guzartiin to ye kehtin rahmatein nazil hon Allah ki Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath yahin qiyam kya tha, un dinon hamarey ( saman ( bahut halkey-phulkey they, sawaariyaan aur zaade-raah ki bhi kami thi, maine, meri behan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne, Zuber aur falan-falan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Umra kya aur jab Baitullah ka tawaaf kar chukey to ( Safa aur Marwa ki saee ke baad) ham halal ho gaey, Haj ka ehram ham ne Sham ko baandha tha."
1797,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi jang ya Haj w Umra se wapas hotey to jab bhi kisi buland jagah ka chadhaao hota to teen martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey aur ye dua padhtey لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له ، Mina padhi. له الملك ، Mina padhi. وله الحمد ، Mina padhi. وهو على كل شىء قدير ، Mina padhi. آيبون تائبون عابدون ساجدون لربنا حامدون ، Mina padhi. صدق الله وعده ونصر عبده وهزم الأحزاب وحدهAllaah ke siwa koi maabood nahi wo akelaa hai uska koi Sharik nahi, mulk usi ka hai aur hamd usi ke liye hai wo har cheez par qaadir hai, ham wapas ho rahe hain, tauba kartey huey ibadat kartey huey apne rab ke huzoor sajda kartey huey aur uski hamd kartey huey, Allah ne apna wada sachcha kar dikhaya , apne bandey ki madad ki aur sarey lashkar ko tanha shikast de di. (fatah Makka ki taraf ishara hai).''"
1798,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif laey to banu- abdul-Muttalib ke chand bachchon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istiqbaal kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik bachchey ko (apni sawari ke) aagey bitha liya aur doosrey ko peechhey."
1799,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka tashrif ley jatey to masjid shajra mein Namaz padhtey aur jab wapas hotey to zul-Hulaifa ki wadi ke nasheb mein Namaz padhtey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah tak saari raat wahin rehtey.
1800,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (safar se) raat ko ghar nahi pahunchtey they ya subah ke waqt pahunch jatey ya do-pahar baad (zawaal se lekar ghurub aaftaab tak kisi bhi waqt tashrif laatey) .
1801,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (safar se) ghar raat ke waqt utarney se mana farmaya,"
1802,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar se Madina wapas hotey aur Madina ke oopri ilaaqon par nazar padtii to apni ontni ko tez kar detey, koi doosra janwar hota to usey bhi eid lagaatey . abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Haaris-bin-Umair ne Humaid se ye lafz zyada kiye hain ke ''Madeena se mohabbat ki wjah se sawari tez kar detey they. ''ham se Quteba ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ismail bin Jafar ne bayan kya, unse Humaid lamba ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unhon-ne ( darjaat ke bajaey) ( جدرات ( kaha, uski mutabiat (pairavi) Haris bin Umer ne ki."
1803,ye aayat hamarey barey mein nazil hui. Ansar jab Haj ke liye aatey to (ehraam ke baad) gharon mein darwazon se nahi jatey balke diiwaaron se kood kar (ghar ke andar) dakhil hua kartey they phir (Islam laney ke baad) aik Ansari shakhs aaya aur darwazey se ghar mein dakhil ho gaya is par logon ne laanat malaamat ki to ye wahiy nazil hui ke ''ye koi neki nahi hai ke gharon mein peechhey se ( diiwaaron par chadh kar) aao balke nek wo shakhs hai jo taqwa ikhtiyar karey aur gharon mein unke darwazon se aaya karo.
1804,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya safar azab ka aik tukda hai, aadmi ko khaney peeney aur soney (har aik cheez ( se rok deta hai, isliye jab koi apni zarurat poori kar chukey to fauran ghar wapas aa jaey."
1805,"main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka ke rastey mein tha ke unhein (apni beewii) Safiya-bint-abii-Ubaid ki sakht bimari ki khabar mili aur wo bahut hi zyada tezi se chalney lagey, phir jab surkhi ghurub ho gaee to sawari se nichey utrey aur maghrib aur isha aik sath mila kar padhin, iske baad farmaya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke jab jaldi chalnaa hota to maghrib mein der karke donon (ishaa aur maghrib) ko aik sath mila kar padhtey they."
